OL,3,CDorries to hand back nearly #17,000
OL,4,Cmistakenly received as severance pay
OL,6,FFormer Tory MP has said she will hand
OL,7,Fback more than #16,000 she mistakenly
OL,8,Freceived in severance pay for being a
OL,9,FCabinet minister.
OL,11,FMs Dorries received the money
OL,12,Ffollowing her tenure as culture
OL,13,Fsecretary under Boris Johnson, but
OL,14,Funder current rules it should not have
OL,15,Fbeen paid.
OL,17,FA departing minister is entitled to
OL,18,Fthree months' salary in lieu of notice
OL,19,Fbut only those under 65 are eligible.
