OL,3,CDorries to hand back nearly #17,000
OL,4,Cmistakenly received as severance pay
OL,6,FMs Dorries turned 65 several months
OL,7,Fbefore leaving her Cabinet role.
OL,9,FSpeaking on the BBC's Sunday With
OL,10,FLaura Kuenssberg, the former minister
OL,11,Fsaid she had only seen an email about
OL,12,Fthe error on Friday and promised to
OL,13,Fpay it back "on Monday morning".
OL,15,F"That means now everybody knows I'm
OL,16,Fnot 49," she joked.
OL,18,F"I'll pay it back on Monday morning,
OL,19,Fthere are no details in the email on
OL,20,Fhow to do that but I will, I'm sure,
OL,21,Ffind out. I was gutted."
