OL,3,CDorries to hand back nearly #17,000
OL,4,Cmistakenly received as severance pay
OL,6,FAs first reported by The Times,
OL,7,Fgovernment accounts show she received
OL,8,F#16,876 as an exit payout following
OL,9,Fher tenure under Mr Johnson.
OL,11,FMs Dorries was MP for Mid Bedfordshire
OL,12,Ffrom 2005 to 2023 before she quit in
OL,13,Fprotest at her exclusion from Mr
OL,14,FJohnson's resignation honours list.
OL,16,FLabour has recently pledged to reform
OL,17,Fministerial severance pay rules if it
OL,18,Fwins power in the election this year
OL,19,Fafter it emerged nearly #1 million was
OL,20,Fspent during last year's political
OL,21,Fturmoil.
