OL,4,Cmistakenly received as severance pay
OL,6,FThe Opposition says it would link
OL,7,Fpayouts to time spent in office so
OL,8,Fthat departing ministers get a quarter
OL,9,Fof their actual earnings over the
OL,10,Fprevious 12 months instead of their
OL,11,Ffinal annual salary.
OL,13,FMinisters who leave their job while
OL,14,Funder investigation for misconduct or
OL,15,Fa breach of the rules would have their
OL,16,Fseverance suspended too, and quashed
OL,17,Fif the claims are upheld under the
OL,18,Fplans.
