OL,6,FThe government did not respond to a
OL,7,Frequest for comment but Cabinet Office
OL,8,Fminister Alex Burghart said earlier
OL,9,Fthis month: "Such payments should not
OL,10,Fapply where a person has attained the
OL,11,Fage of 65.
OL,13,F"If a former minister was incorrectly
OL,14,Fgiven a severance payment, the
OL,15,Frelevant department will contact the
OL,16,Findividual to recover the over-
OL,17,Fpayment."
